    The GenericFileImporter class imports a tab delimited file containing the following columns: - Accession : a unique protein identifier - Description : description of the protein.

    TP1dScorer
    TP1dScorer Score for 1D TP datasets based on thermal shift and quality of curve fit.
    TP1DUserInterface
    TP1DUserInterface The TP1DUserInterface class creates the default tab that opens when a Protein1D Proteome object is loaded into TPMAP It constructs a BorderPane with properties on the left, protein table, fold change table and melt curve chart in the center and downstream analysis options on the right.
    TP2dDestabilisationScorer

    TP2dMeanFC Calculates the mean abundance-dependent fold change of a protein in a 2d thermal profiling experiment.

    TP2DMedianNormalisation Normalise proteins by the median value among all proteins
    TP2dStabilisationScorer
    TP2dStabilisationScorer TPMAP algorithm for identifying stabilized proteins in 2d thermal profiling experiments.
    TP2DUserInterface
    TP2DUserInterface The TP2DUserInterface class creates the default tab that opens when a Protein2D Proteome object is loaded into TPMAP It constructs a BorderPane with properties on the left, protein table and abundance fold change table in the center and downstream analysis options on the right.
    TPBootstrapAnalysis
    TPBootstrapAnalysis Runs a bootstrap analysis for 2D TP datasets.
